Package frogger.model

Class GameModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • frogger.model.GameModel
  • public class GameModel
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    scyyx1 Represent the game model of game world. Set up the frogger and some game status of the game. Contains methods to initialize all status in game and update the status.
